Lua 5.2.1 build for Android.

Pre-requisites: Android NDK (http://developer.android.com/tools/sdk/ndk/index.html)

Based on the following post: http://www.badlogicgames.com/wordpress/?p=943 (for Lua 5.1.4)

How to build: go to the project folder, open the command line and type: (path to NDK)/ndk-build

Original Lua readme:
--------------------

This is Lua 5.2.1, released on 08 Jun 2012.

For installation instructions, license details, and
further information about Lua, see doc/readme.html.

